data.description: Check out this fantastic country-style home in Lockesburg, Arkansas! With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1740 sqft of space, it's perfect for a cozy and comfortable lifestyle. The 8 acres of land and the pond add a touch of nature and tranquility. Plus, being outside the city limits gives you a peaceful retreat. The modern feel of the house adds a stylish touch. This property is definitely a gem!
